    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = 0.56
    v1 = v1
    v2 = 0.85
    v0 = (v2 * (0.04 - (v1 + 0.49 + v0 + 0.95)))
    v2 = v2
    v0 = (wp.sin((v1 + 0.81 / v1 + 0.31)) + wp.sin((tmp + 0.59 * tmp + 0.97)))
    tmp = (wp.sin(wp.abs(v0 + 0.36)) + v0)
    data[tid] = v0
